	<h1 style="background-color:#ff0000;">Vampires are Real</h1>
	<h2>A website dedicated to revealing the TRUTH</h2>

	<img src="vampire.jpg" alt="Rare photo caught of a vampire />

	<p>Many people ask me why I have dedicated my entire life's work to the mystery of the vampire. They say: "there are so many more pressing issues!", "you have no hard evidence!", "vampires are the least of our worries against the existential threats of nuclear war, global warming, and artificial intelligence", but I know better my friends.
This guide has been divided into lessons. You should read them chronologically; however, in emergencies, I understand one particular lesson can mean the difference between life and death for amateurs</p>

	<hr />

